urls.title: New Zealand isn’t just flattening the curve. It’s squashing it.
urls.description: The number of new coronavirus cases is starting to decline as the country pursues a policy of elimination rather than containment.

text:
In stark contrast to other western countries, New Zealand abruptly went into complete lockdown and is going for the "elimination," not the "containment," of the coronavirus. It looks like it's working:

https://t.co/xF24X6ZRLs
